Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining　夏の午後に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}通り雨　傘の下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing　濡れた頬に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そっと口づけた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:41.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あの季節にまだ焦がれている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:50.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何も手につかずに　上の空の日々
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:55.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:22:01.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}まだ足りなくて　まだ消えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:07.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}重ねた手のひらから幼さが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:19.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そんなフレーズに濡れてく雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:25.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ足りなくて　まだ言えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}数えた日の夢からさよならが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:35.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:38.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:46.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}触れられずにいれたら　笑えたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.59,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining 夏日的午後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.76,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雨來了又去 留我在傘下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.85,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing 沾濕的臉{\fn方正隶变_GBK\bord0.3\b0\fscy113\fscx105}頰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.98,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}輕輕一吻 現了紅霞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:41.86,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}四季更了又替 不變的是焦急的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:50.24,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我無心做任何事情 心中想的一直是{\fn方正隶变_GBK\bord0.3\b0\fscy113\fscx105}你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:55.21,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:22:01.34,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還想再索取一點 還感覺隱隱若現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:07.68,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}十指相扣 掌心微熱 是{\fn方正隶变_GBK\bord0.3\b0\fscy113\fscx105}你{\r}青澀的熾烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.60,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.68,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:19.77,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一字一句沁我心 像身旁飄落的雨點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:25.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只想再索取一點 告別梗在了嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.16,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}細數曾經滿懷憧憬追逐夢想的當年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:35.33,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:38.37,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:46.51,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果不能伸手觸摸 是否還能保持笑臉?
